<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
  <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
  {% include "./partials/header.njk" %}
  <main>
    {%for data in tickerData -%}
      <div class="bg-gray-100 my-10 border-indigo-600  | p-4 border-solid rounded-3xl border-2 | flex justify-around cursor-pointer">
      <div class="flex flex-col text-center content-center justify-center">
        <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">{{data.name}}</p>
        <p class="text-black text-justify font-semibold">â‚¬{{data.current_price}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    {%-endfor%}
    {% include "./partials/discover-trending.njk" %}

    <section class="bg-site-secondary-bg">
    <div class="whyarlan bg-site-secondary-bg container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-xl text-left md:text-center md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold py-8">Why choose Arlan?</h2>
      <p class="hidden md:block text-center w-2/5 m-auto mb-10">We believe that every person, no matter their experience or skills should be able to purchase cryptocurrencies. That's why we use a simple system, to make it as easy as possible, yet still secure and competitive with the rest.</p>
      <div class="discover__list flex flex-wrap m-auto md:justify-between">
        <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4 mb-12 rounded-xl">
          <div class="list__item--content p-4">
            <img src="media/whyarlan/safe.png" class="m-auto -mt-12"/>
            <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Safe</h3>
            <p>With countell checks and the latest technologies, your transactions are secured on multiple levels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4 mb-12 rounded-xl">
          <div class="list__item--content p-4">
            <img src="media/whyarlan/simple.png" class="m-auto -mt-12" />
            <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Simple</h3>
            <p>We strive to make out platform easy to use, so anybody can get involved in investing and start making money from it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4  mb-12 rounded-xl">
          <div class="list__item--content p-4">
            <img src="media/whyarlan/competitive.png" class="m-auto -mt-12"/>
            <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Competitive</h3>
            <p>Because we're able to sell packets of coins, we are able to sell at a very competitive price compared to other platforms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </section>

    {% include "./partials/cryptocurrencies.njk" %}
  </main>
    {% include "./partials/footer.njk" %}
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/eefbba8f9b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>